maml:description.maml:para: Get geo replication link for Redis Cache.

There are four different ways to get geo-replication link detail. Either provide parameter Name or PrimaryServerName and/or SecondaryServerName. Name is given then all link where cache exists will be returned. If only PrimaryServerName is given then all links where cache is primary will be returned. Standard and Premium tiers. - hash-max-ziplist-value. Configures memory optimization for small aggregate data types. Standard and Premium tiers. - set-max-intset-entries. Standard and Premium tiers. - zset-max-ziplist-value. Configures memory optimization for small aggregate data types. Standard and Premium tiers. - databases. Configures the number of databases.
